    "\"Basically, yes. Which wouldn't have been such a big deal, except that Cadeaux was pretending to be female students, which made Galloway out to be some sort of predatory lesbian. Now, Chicago doesn't mind predators; lesbians, that's another story. So Chicago launches this whole investigation into Galloway, who might actually have been a lesbian, just not the predatory kind, and so she gets so scared off that she rescinds her job application, and Cadeaux gets the job, and no one knew any better until word got out he was bragging about it to graduate students at the pub. He'd made the whole thing up. He'd got his mum and sisters to handwrite anonymous letters and everything. Galloway found out and swore she'd ruin his career, except she died in a car accident before anyone could get to the bottom of things.\"",
