  "\"The next chance you have, look up at the night sky. It's missing a constellation. A bridge is broken.\" Her sash collapsed. \"Darkness, now.\"",
  "",
  "\"Haven't you ever tried to find him?\" asked Peter.",
  "\"We aren't allowed, dear boy. And in any case, he would not know me. He's washed all memory of me out of his mind.\"",
  "\"Oh,\" said Peter. \"I'm sorry.\"",
  "\"You're so sweet.\" The Weaver Girl reached out and tweaked his nose.",
