  "“Who’s your advisor?”",
  "",
  "Alice found it prudent to lie.",
  "“Helen Murray.”",
  "",
  "“And she makes your life hard, does she?”",
  "",
  "“Some.”",
  "",
  "“Hm.",
  "Well, see, my advisor was Jacob Grimes.",
  "I’m sure you’ve heard of him.”",
  "",
  "“Haven’t we all.”",
