  "“Thank you.",
  "I appreciate it.”",
  "",
  "“Anytime, love.",
  "Get some sleep.”",
  "",
  "Elspeth vanished into the stacks.",
  "Alice curled in on her side and rested her cheek against the shelves, listening to Elspeth’s rattling footsteps disappearing up the stairs.",
  "She was cold; the air below deck felt stale and drafty at once.",
