"Ramanujan’s Summation.",
"Setiya’s Modifications.",
"Two columns knocked together then in his head; two premises that concluded with his redemption; at that moment, the only valid thing in the world.",
"",
"First: Alice Law was headed to Hell.",
"",
"Second: he must go with her."
